room_title: Escape room "Revenge" by Bayou Escape Rooms in Lake Charles
room_address: 1440 W McNeese St Lake Charles, LA 70605
room_description: It’s time for your 30-year class reunion at Myrtle Springs High School. Elliott Kingsley, one of your former classmates, is now the principal and he has big plans for this reunion. Some people just can’t let go of the past…
